He lunges with a short-handled spear -

ARAGORN

For my people!

It takes Ma-Gog in the gut. His one eye bulges. Aragorn rips the spear out
-

ARAGORN (CONT'D)

And this - for my daughterl He drives the spear into the High Priest's
